overview:
Himachalhotels is a one stop government authorized travel company catering to all travel related needs for Himachal.

The company offers tailormade and readymade tour packages for Himachal ranging from honeymoon packages, religious tours, adventure sports and weekend tour packages in some of the most beautiful destinations Shimla, Kasauli, Dharamshala, Mcleodganj, Kullu, Manali, Dalhousie, Chamba etc.
